We climbed down the side of the mountain which was, interesting, and then went under the waterfall which was so cool. Climbed back up then went to the top of the falls which was crazyyy. Christa and I swam in the river for a little bit then went back and took naps til dinner time. When it got dark we all went down near the river and had a bonfire.
